description: Sonic and the rest of his family head to the beach for a family outting. While there, Sonic decides that it's now or never, and he must learn to swim TODAY. His lover, Bartleby will do whatever he can to help his bitch. Their friends, Knuckles and Mindy, as well as Robotnik, sleet and Dingo are all there to cheer the small, fat, blue man on in his en devours.
creator: A Beautiful Tomorrow
